                         CALL FOR PARTICIPATION

                               TLDI 2009

                         ACM SIGPLAN Workshop on
              Types in Language Design and Implementation

                            24 January 2009
                         Savannah, Georgia, USA

               To be held in conjunction with POPL 2009

               http://ttic.uchicago.edu/~amal/tldi2009/
